message.content: cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DL. The paper discusses a methodology for ranking and summarizing scientific abstracts based on annotated corpora, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This falls under the sub-field of information retrieval (cs.IR) and also involves aspects of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL).
